Instructions to Compile and Run Mine Detection Code

Dependencies


1. move-base package - sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-move-base
2. teb-local-planner package - sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-teb-local-planner


Instructions

1. Compile the given src in a workspace(catkin_make)

2. Make the following python scripts executables( Run command sudo chmod +x * )

Location: src/my_code/scripts

goals.py, mine_obstacles.py, mine_transform.py


3. Run the following command to launch the code( Simulator launch is also added to the launch file)

roslaunch hratc2017_framework bring_up.launch 

